    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "The Stranger I met in #m10003004# is, surprisingly, a ghost! She remained in the hospital, unaware that she had died, waiting for Naora to return... Now unwilling to accept her death, she told me that in order to live again, she needs me to defeat #b50 #o21#s#k and collect #b25 #t4000020#s#k. She asked for my help one last time. I wonder if that’s really all it takes to bring her back..."
    },
    "2": {
      "_dirName": "2",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "#p412# who I met in #m10003004# was a ghost. She was staying in the Hospital, not knowing that she was dead. She couldn't live again with #t4000020#. It seems that she already knew she couldn't make it... I really hope she finds peace."
    },
