  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Ah... this may be a little cracked, but I can definitely see myself with it."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Thank you so much. I need to get out of here as soon as I get these bandages off. It's waaay too cold in here."
      },
      "2": {
        "_dirName": "2",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "What the! No way! What... what happened here?? Why can't I see myself through the mirror? Did I... die?????? No way, that can't be true! I can't be dead yet! Hey there, please help me out once more!"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "When you defeat #r#o21#s#k, they drop something called #b#t4000020##k, and from what I've heard, it has the power to revive the dead. Please #rdefeat 50 #o21#s#k and bring me #b25 #t4000020##k! If I can get them, I might be able to come back from the dead..."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "How can you be so cold! I'll be cursing you forever!"
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Ahh, thanks for getting me the charms. I can't believe you got me all that... Well, I have to be honest with you. Even with those charms, I don't think I'll be coming back to life."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Even if I come back alive with these charms, I won't be fully alive, per se, kind of like a zombie. I can't believe I figured this out just now... but I will never forget the fact that you took great lengths to help me out. Thank you so so much."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Do you like the cape that I gave you? It's a cape made of the devastating powers of the #t4000020#. I'll see you... around... somewhere... somehow ..."
        }
      },
